New Zealand Bus Passes





Flexible Itinerary Options

 
Our most popular transport passes for independent travellers.  'Travel like a local' NZ's largest Hop-on/Hop-off network.  Total freedom + sightseeing & activity options.




Fixed Itinerary Passes

 
Pre-planned transport passes for those wanting a set itinerary travel.  Choose from a range of passes including sightseeing tour options.




InterCity Commuter
Save up to 38%* on regular fares between Hamilton/Auckland.  Over 20 services per day between cities on NZ's #1 Bus Network.




Student Passes

 
Great savings for students!  Passes available for Hawke's Bay, New Plymouth and Dunedin students.
